OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sun 5 Jul to Tue 14 Jul
OL,6,FHigh pressure will dominate across
OL,7,FEngland and Wales over the weekend and
OL,8,Finto next week. This will bring dry
OL,9,Fand warm conditions with plenty of
OL,10,Fsunshine for most. Scotland and
OL,11,FNorthern Ireland will probably see
OL,12,Fmore cloud, with periods of rain at
OL,13,Ftimes, mainly affecting western
OL,14,FScotland. Through next week the high
OL,15,Fpressure may extend northwards at
OL,16,Ftimes to bring periods of drier and
OL,17,Fwarmer weather to Scotland and
OL,18,FNorthern Ireland. Winds will be light
OL,19,Fto moderate for most, though stronger
OL,20,Faround northern hills and coasts near
OL,21,Flow pressure systems. Temperatures
OL,22,Fwill rise through the early part of
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,23,Fthe period, becoming very warm or hot
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
OL,24,Fin parts of the south and east.
